					<div id="interfaces">
						<p>Welcome to CC+, a relational database of coiled-coil structures!</p>
						<p>This database has been developed to help probe our understanding of the sequence-to-structure relationships in coiled-coil protein structures. To cite the database &#8212; published <a href="http://nar.oxfordjournals.org/content/vol37/suppl_1/index.dtl">here</a> &#8212; please refer to <a href="http://www.chm.bris.ac.uk/org/woolfson/publications.html#abstract64">Testa <i>et al.</i> NAR, 2008</a>. To cite the Periodic Table of Coiled-Coil Protein Structures, please refer to <a href="http://www.chm.bris.ac.uk/org/woolfson/publications.html#65">Moutevelis &amp; Woolfson, JMB, 2008</a>.</p>
						<h1>How would you like to search for coiled coils?</h1>
						<ul>
							<li>
								<a title="Periodic table of coiled-coil architectures" href="http://coiledcoils.chm.bris.ac.uk/ccplus/search/periodic_table">
									<em>Periodic table of coiled-coil architectures</em>
									<img src="http://coiledcoils.chm.bris.ac.uk/ccplus/images/system/periodic_table.gif" alt=""/>
									Browse the variety of coiled-coil architectures using a pictorial approach.
								</a>
							</li>
							<li>
								<a title="Dynamic search of coiled-coil assignments" href="http://coiledcoils.chm.bris.ac.uk/ccplus/search/dynamic_interface">
									<em>Dynamic search of coiled-coil assignments</em>
									<img src="http://coiledcoils.chm.bris.ac.uk/ccplus/images/system/dynamic_interface.gif" alt=""/>
									Compile a dataset of coiled-coil assignments with an easy-to-use interface.
								</a>
							</li>
